"      Goedert JJ, Vitale F, Lauria C, et al, &ldquo;Risk Factors for Classical Kaposi's Sarcoma,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       J Natl Cancer Inst",
"      </i>",
"      , 2002, 94(22):1712-8.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"UTD.htm?13/39/13940/abstract-text/12441327/pubmed\" id=\"12441327\" target=\"_blank\">",
